g.text: Mavenlink has created a different approach for successfully running Services. One that transcends the traditional bounds of project management software. By bridging core planning, project accounting, analysis, collaboration and project management systems in a single Operational System of Record, organizations are able to experience dramatically improved visibility, predictability, and agility at a lower cost.
Unify resource management, project management, business intelligence, project accounting, and team collaboration to establish a single source of truth and vivid insights.
